# Code Owners
# GitHub will automatically request review from these owners when a PR
# touches files in their area.
# Syntax: <pattern>  <@github-username or @org/team>
# Replace @your-github-username with your actual GitHub username.

# Global fallback – everything requires owner review
*                           @your-github-username

# Frontend
frontend/                   @your-github-username

# Backend
backend/                    @your-github-username

# CI/CD – only the owner can change pipelines
.github/                    @your-github-username

# Root config files
package.json                @your-github-username
vercel.json                 @your-github-username
